21
0:00:59.024,000 --> 0:01:01,000
Here I am alone in my office, but I'm not alone at all.

22
0:01:01.76,000 --> 0:01:04,000
I'm connected to 80,000 people around the world,

23
0:01:05.32,000 --> 0:01:08,000
and that's four Madison Square Gardens

24
0:01:08.697,000 --> 0:01:09,000
full of cousins.

25
0:01:10.412,000 --> 0:01:12,000
And some of them are going to be great,

26
0:01:13.349,000 --> 0:01:15,000
