and then you combine and combine and combine

44
0:02:02.01,000 --> 0:02:03,000
until you get these massive,

45
0:02:03.911,000 --> 0:02:04,000
mega-family trees

46
0:02:05.761,000 --> 0:02:07,000
with thousands of people on them,

47
0:02:08.262,000 --> 0:02:09,000
or even millions.

48
0:02:09.677,000 --> 0:02:11,000
I'm on something on Geni called

49
0:02:12.004,000 --> 0:02:13,000
the world family tree,

50
0:02:13.93,000 --> 0:02:15,000
which has no less than a jaw-dropping

51
0:02:16.487,000 --> 0:02:19,000
75 million people.

52
0:02:20.017,000 --> 0:02:23,000
