53
0:02:23.857,000 --> 0:02:25,000
or marriage, sometimes both.

54
0:02:26.337,000 --> 0:02:28,000
(Laughter)

55
0:02:28.904,000 --> 0:02:32,000
It's in all seven continents, including Antarctica.

56
0:02:33.089,000 --> 0:02:35,000
