0:03:46.82,000 --> 0:03:47,000
But does it really matter?

84
0:03:48.613,000 --> 0:03:49,000
What's the importance?

85
0:03:49.955,000 --> 0:03:5,000
And I do think it is important,

86
0:03:51.633,000 --> 0:03:53,000
