0:04:03.976,000 --> 0:04:05,000
about how diseases are inherited,

91
0:04:06.125,000 --> 0:04:07,000
how people migrate,

92
0:04:07.993,000 --> 0:04:09,000
and there's a team of scientists at MIT right now

93
0:04:10.913,000 --> 0:04:12,000
studying the world family tree.

94
0:04:13.593,000 --> 0:04:15,000
