126
0:05:43.605,000 --> 0:05:44,000
So in 10, 12 generations,

127
0:05:45.298,000 --> 0:05:47,000
you're going to have thousands of offspring,

128
0:05:47.429,000 --> 0:05:48,000
and millions of offspring.

129
0:05:48.946,000 --> 0:05:49,000
